      'projects.pwc.desc':      'Solo submission for PwC "Reinvent Operations" (VivaTech 2026). LP model minimizing logistics cost across Morocco\'s petroleum distribution network (refineries → depots → endpoints), combined with an LSTM demand forecasting layer. Grounded in direct knowledge of Morocco\'s hydrocarbon sector structure.',
